<section xmlns="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook" xml:id="part-ii-comprehensive-statutory-gap-analysis-of-the-term-patron">
  <title>
    <emphasis role="strong">Part II: Comprehensive Statutory Gap
    Analysis of the Term "Patron"</emphasis>
  </title>
  <para>
      This section directly addresses the completeness of the original
      document by providing a definitive, cross-referenced inventory of
      California Code sections containing the word "patron."
      It validates the thoroughness of the initial research while
      identifying and analyzing the few statutes that were not included.
    </para>
